text: Henry Gramajo (born 19 September 1970) is a Uruguayan equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Uruguayan male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Uruguay Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
